name: Tellers Details Report
query:
SELECT
`tabUser`.full_name as "Teller Name::200",
`tabTransactions Details`.mctn as "MCTN::150",
`tabTransactions Details`.currency as "Currency:150",
`tabTransactions Details`.posting_date as "Posting Date::120", 
`tabTransactions Details`.outflow as "Withdraw:Currency:150",
`tabTransactions Details`.inflow as "Deposit::Currency:150",
`tabTransactions Details`.description as "Transaction Desc::200"
FROM
`tabTransactions Details`, `tabAgents`, `tabUser`
WHERE
`tabTransactions Details`.user_id = `tabAgents`.agent_user
AND
`tabAgents`.agent_user = `tabUser`.email
ORDER BY 
`tabUser`.full_name ASC
